title: Force of Evil (1948 Film-Noir) John Garfield’s brotherhood unravels in the underworld

sources.title: Force of Evil (1948 Film-Noir) John Garfield’s brotherhood unravels in the underworld
sources.description:
Joe Morse (John Garfield), a sharp-tongued lawyer, dives deep into the numbers racket to help his brother Leo (Thomas Gomez) but ends up entangled in a web of betrayal and greed. As the stakes rise, Joe must outmaneuver ruthless gangsters and his own moral collapse to survive the fallout.

Original title: Force of Evil
Alternative title: The Numbers Racke / Tucker's People

Director: Abraham Polonsky
Writers: Abraham PolonskyIra Wolfert

Main cast
John Garfield - Joe Morse
Beatrice Pearson - Doris Lowry
Thomas Gomez - Leo Morse
Marie Windsor - Edna Tucker
Howland Chamberlain - Frederick "Freddie" Bauer
Roy Roberts - Ben Tucker
Paul Fix - Bill Ficco
Stanley Prager - Wally
Barry Kelley - Det. Egan

Genres: Film Noir, Crime, Drama
Release date: December 25, 1948
Filming location: New York City


Availability varies by region
